Preheat oven to 300 degrees F. Beat egg white and sugar in large bowl with wire whisk until foamy. Stir in orange and lemon peels, cinnamon and cloves. Add cereal and nut mix; toss to evenly coat. Spread evenly into lightly greased 15x10x1-inch baking pan. Bake 20 to 25 min. or until toasted and dry, stirring occasionally. Cool completely. Store in tightly covered container at room temperature.